#, fuzzy
msgid "free culture"
msgstr "fri kultur"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><indexterm><secondary>
#, fuzzy
msgid "commercial vs. noncommercial"
msgstr "kommerciel versus ikke-kommerciel"

